---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | RelayLaunch"
  description="Terms and conditions for using the RelayLaunch website and digital infrastructure services. Covers service agreements, intellectual property, client work ownership, and governing law."
  canonicalUrl="https://www.relaylaunch.com/terms/"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: 'https://www.relaylaunch.com/' },
    { name: 'Terms of Service', url: 'https://www.relaylaunch.com/terms/' },
  ]}
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 740px;">
      <h1 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Last updated: March 11, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using the RelayLaunch website (relaylaunch.com), you agree to be bound by these terms of service. If you do not agree, please do not use our website.</p>

        <h2>Services</h2>
        <p>RelayLaunch LLC provides digital infrastructure consulting services including website development, workflow automation, email marketing, and ongoing operations support. Service details, deliverables, and pricing are outlined in individual service agreements.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, and design, is the property of RelayLaunch LLC and protected by applicable copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without written permission.</p>

        <h2>Client Work</h2>
        <p>Work product created for clients is governed by individual service agreements. Unless otherwise specified, clients retain ownership of custom deliverables upon full payment.</p>

        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>RelayLaunch LLC provides this website and its content "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of this website or our services beyond the amount paid for the specific service in question.</p>

        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Commonwealth of Massachusetts. Any disputes will be resolved in the courts of Middlesex County, Massachusetts.</p>

        <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>RelayLaunch LLC</strong><br />
        Watertown, MA<br />
        <a href="mailto:hello@relaylaunch.com">hello@relaylaunch.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .prose p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
